OL,3,CFormer Guernsey Chief Minister dies
OL,4,Caged 83
OL,6,FFormer Guernsey Chief Minister Mike
OL,7,FTorode has died aged 83.
OL,9,FHis family say he passed away
OL,10,Fpeacefully on Tuesday 3 September and
OL,11,Fa funeral service will be held at St
OL,12,FMartin's Parish Church at 1pm on
OL,13,FThursday 12 September - those who knew
OL,14,Fhim are invited to attend.
OL,16,FMr Torode was in Guernsey politics for
OL,17,F33 years, becoming one of the longest-
OL,18,Fserving States Members as he was first
OL,19,Felected Deputy for St Martin's in
OL,20,FApril 1979.
