OL,6,FHe later became a Deputy for the South
OL,7,FEast of the island in 2004 and Home
OL,8,FAffairs Minister before being elected
OL,9,Ffor the top politicial job in March
OL,10,F2007 - leaving the job of Chief
OL,11,FMinister at the end of his term in
OL,12,F2008.
OL,14,FHome Affairs Committee President
OL,15,FDeputy Rob Prow says: "I was truly
OL,16,Fsaddened to hear of the passing of
OL,17,Fformer Deputy Mike Torode, a man whom
OL,18,FI knew for the majority of my adult
OL,19,Flife.
