OL,6,F"We first met when I was a Customs
OL,7,FOfficer and he was working for British
OL,8,FMidlands Airways at the Airport and
OL,9,Ffrom that point, right up until our
OL,10,Fmost recent interactions, he was
OL,11,Frespectful, straight-down-the-line and
OL,12,Fdedicated to Guernsey.
OL,14,F"Mike had a very long history of
OL,15,Fservice to this island. He was the
OL,16,FMinister for Home Affairs for a term,
OL,17,Fduring which I served as his Chief
OL,18,FCustoms Officer.
