OL,3,CFormer Guernsey Chief Minister dies
OL,4,Caged 83
OL,6,F"He was a huge advocate for the
OL,7,FDepartment's Professional Services,
OL,8,Fshowing constant support for officers
OL,9,Fand a genuine interest in their work.
OL,10,FHe still has an impact on the police
OL,11,Fto this day as he formally opened the
OL,12,Fcurrent police station.
OL,14,F"Guernsey has lost one of its
OL,15,Fstrongest characters with Mike's
OL,16,Fpassing and he will undoubtedly be
OL,17,Fmissed by so many. He will also be
OL,18,Fremembered, however, for the way he
OL,19,Fconducted himself in public service,
OL,20,Fhis tenacity and for the examples he
OL,21,Fset."
